Initial Release!

This release includes:

* Ability to create a static site
* Compatibility with relative URLs
* Filter posts based on YAML meta tags
* Set the start and length of pages
* Instant Search
* Gruntfile Integration with a number of tasks such as Sass, JSHint, JSONLint
* Grunt tasks for production (including compression)
